answers.answer: I was sent from my doctors appointment to the hospital in an ambulance for these symptoms. I had preeclampsia. Not saying you do but if you have headaches too or even see like floaters you should call your doctor asap. Keep an eye on your BP! Trust me you don't want the magnesium drip :p

question: And protein in my urine. Midwife says this could be early signs of labour. Any ideas on how to make it progress? Im really over being pregnant..has anyone else had these symptoms and gone into labour ?
